title: Full Show (Mahomes beats Brady, Cooper Rush shines for Cowboys, Baker loses again)
description:

1:35:56 The latest Antonio Brown controversy
1:44:40 Lakers Big 3 has a new mantra
1:50:54 Packers come back to beat Patriots in OT
1:55:29 Rams vs 49ers on MNF
